metadata.name: When is Love?
metadata.description:
When does love feel like love?
When does it become special?
Is it the person? Is it the place?
It's time. It's when time makes every fleeting second feel special as you know that it will never come back again. 
The clock at the foreground is a reminder that love is special as long as time is present to add value to it.

Dimension: 1080 x 1080
Format: MP4
Utility: 1 Desktop Wallpaper (1920 x 1080)
